#       Setting the baee

# We have been using Terraform to create and manage resources for a specific provider.
# Organizations would end-to-end solution for creations for infrastructure and confoguring appropriate packages required of the application
# Provisioners are used to execute scripts on a local or remote machine as part of resource creation or destruction
# Example: After Vm is launched, install software package reuired for application

# 2 major Types of Provisioners
# local-exec remote-exec

# local-exec invokes a local executamle after  resource is created
# Example fetch IP address and store in ip.txt

# remote-exec provisioners allow to invoke scripts or run commands directly on the remote server
# Example after EC2 is launched, install nginx